::Installation of RESTful-TTS::

- Download the RESTful-TTS folder and place it in the live or ww folder of your PHP server.

- Enable mod_rewrite in your Apache/server.

- Make the folders in the application writable by Apache.

- Install LAME in your Mac by visiting http://sourceforge.net/projects/lame/files/lame/. 
LAME is required for format conversion to mp3.

- sqlite and say are assumed to be built-in on your Mac.

::Using RESTful-TTS

- Do a GET or a POST on http://your-server/RESTful-TTS/converter/

 Eg. http://localhost/RESTful-TTS/converter/hello gives you an audio response of the text "hello"

